robocode.control.events.IBattleListener
public class AESIFitnessFunction
extends java.lang.Object
implements robocode.control.events.IBattleListener

The class that evaluates a population and assigns fitness values but also compiles chromosomes. This class has a lot of "unimplemented" overridden methods that are of no use for us.
